data.description: Absolutely breathtaking remodel. Better than new, with all ultra modern features. Luxury kitchen and bathrooms, all new flooring, lighting. High end modern fixtures. Induction cooktop. Electrolux convection oven/microwave. Large loft office overlooking your enormous family room with  fireplace and vaulted ceiling. Tall ceilings throughout with a first floor master, 2 car garage, fully fenced in yard, large closets in every bedroom. Tremendous value for the price. The list just goes on and on of the upgrades in this completely custom and unique home. This is an absolute must see, shows fantastic in person. Listing agent has an interest in this property.
